==Ancient Greek==

===Etymology===
*Apparently a primary word, including the comparative (second form); small (in size, quantity, number or (figuratively) dignity): 

===Pronunciation===
*μικρός, μικρότερος / mikros  mikroteros / mik-ros', mik-rot'-er-os

===Adjective===
'''μικρός'''

# least, less, [[little]], [[small]].

